==Useful Info==
'''Electroferric vorticies''' spawn when you kill enemies with the [[Magnavolt]] spell. The vorticies count as a magnetised monster for the spell, allowing arcs of electricity to be fired at them.

==History==
*Initially, electroferric vorticies were a part of the Magnavolt spell in [[trunk]], but they were simplified away before the [[0.32]] release.
